readme:
Code for Evaluating software-based fingerprint liveness detection using Convolutional Networks and Local Binary Patterns

Use run_convnet.py to train and test using the convolutional neural net pipeline.
Use run_lbp.py to train and test using the LBP pipeline.


For more information about this work, check:

http://arxiv.org/abs/1508.00537
or
http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/login.jsp?tp=&arnumber=6951531&url=http%3A%2F%2Fieeexplore.ieee.org%2Fxpls%2Fabs_all.jsp%3Farnumber%3D6951531
